json.text: Hi and welcome to AC News!
Here’s today’s video clip, movie news are coming up!
Red 2 sees reunited actors Bruce Willis from the first movie and Helen Mirren.
But it also casts Catherine Zeta Jones, Byung Hu (bìanghàn), Mary Louis Parker and John Malkovich.
The plot is obviously the sequel to the first, and it sees the retired team of the CIA
come back with an old school plan to take down new enemies.
The movie is out in theatres August 2nd 2013, directed by Dean Parisot and
with a screenplay by Erich and Jon Hoeber.
Willis is yet to be seen in various projects: Moonrise Kingdom, Looper and A Good Day to Die.
